What you need to know:

United advanced to the May 26 showdown with Villarreal in Gdansk 8-5 on aggregate despite losing 3-2 to Roma in their semi-final second leg at the Stadio Olimpico.And now his players have to face the prospect of four Premier League fixtures in 10 days after Edinson Cavani's brace staved off a valiant attempt at a comeback from their Italian opposition.Cavani's goals in the 39th and 68th minutes ensured United's place in the final, the Uruguayan having also struck a double at Old Trafford.